data.description: Don't miss this incredible home, with original details and beautifully done modern updates. Gorgeous original woodwork and floors, pocket door, stained glass window, decorative fireplace, updated front porch, and more! This 3 bedroom, 1 full (huge!) bathroom is on a one-way street that includes a fully fenced in yard and 2 car detached garage. There's a large green space out front to enjoy too! Awesome location with close proximity to multiple major highways, The Ohio State University and downtown, just to name a few. Newer roof, furnace, water heater, updated wiring and mechanical panels too.
